Stuart Lindsell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stuart_Lindsell 0 Stuart Lindsell (born Reginald Stuart Lindsell, 18 July 1892, Biggleswade, Bedfordshire – 9 July 1969, London) was a British actor, often seen in upper-class roles. He was sometimes credited as R. Stuart Lindsell.
